quran[13]{c,v,t,f}:
  43,48,"A kò níí fi àmì kan hàn wọ́n àyàfi kí ó tóbi ju irú rẹ̀ (tó ṣíwájú). A sì fi ìyà jẹ wọ́n nítorí kí wọ́n lè ṣẹ́rí padà (síbi òdodo).",""
  43,49,"Wọ́n sì wí pé: “Ìwọ òpìdán, pe Olúwa rẹ fún wa nítorí àdéhùn tí Ó ṣe pẹ̀lú rẹ. Dájúdájú àwa máa tẹ̀lé ìmọ̀nà Rẹ̀.”",""
  43,50,"Ṣùgbọ́n nígbà tí A bá mú ìyà kúrò fún wọn, nígbà náà ni wọ́n tún ń yẹ àdéhùn.",""
  43,51,"Fir‘aon sì pèpè láààrin àwọn ènìyàn rẹ̀, ó wí pé: “Ẹ̀yin ènìyàn mi, ṣé tèmi kọ́ ni ìjọba Misrọ àti àwọn odò wọ̀nyí tó ń ṣàn nísàlẹ̀ (ọ̀dọ̀) mi? Ṣé ẹ kò ríran ni?",""
  43,52,"Tàbí ṣé èmi kò lóore ju èyí tí ó jẹ́ ọ̀lẹ ẹni yẹpẹrẹ, tí ó fẹ́ẹ̀ má lè dá ọ̀rọ̀ sọ yanjú?",""
  43,53,"Kí ni kò jẹ́ kí wọ́n fún un ní àwọn ẹ̀gbà-ọwọ́ góòlù tàbí (kí ni kò jẹ́ kí) àwọn mọlāika wá pẹ̀lú rẹ̀, kí wọ́n jẹ́ alábàárìn (tí wọn yóò máa jẹ́rìí rẹ̀)?”",""
  43,54,"Nítorí náà, ó sọ àwọn ènìyàn rẹ̀ di òpè. Wọ́n sì tẹ̀lé e. Dájúdájú wọ́n jẹ́ ìjọ òbìlẹ̀jẹ́.",""
  43,55,"Nígbà tí wọ́n wá ìbínú Wa, A gba ẹ̀san (ìyà) lára wọn. Nítorí náà, A tẹ gbogbo wọn rì (sínú agbami odò).",""
  43,56,"A sì ṣe wọ́n ní ìjọ aṣíwájú (nínú ìparun) àti àpẹ̀ẹrẹ (fèyíkọ́gbọ́n) fún àwọn ẹni ìkẹ́yìn.",""
  43,57,"Nígbà tí àwọn ọ̀ṣẹbọ fi ọmọ Mọryam ṣe àpẹ̀ẹrẹ (fún òrìṣà wọn), nígbà náà ni àwọn ènìyàn rẹ bá ń fi (àpẹ̀ẹrẹ náà) rẹ́rìn-ín.",""
  43,58,"Wọ́n sì wí pé: “Ṣé àwọn òrìṣà wa l’ó lóore jùlọ ni tàbí òun? Wọn kò wulẹ̀ fi ṣàpẹ̀ẹrẹ fún ọ bí kò ṣe (fún) àtakò. Àní sẹ́, ìjọ oníyànjíjà ni wọ́n.",""
  43,59,"Kí ni òun bí kò ṣe ẹrúsìn kan tí A ṣe ìdẹ̀ra fún. A sì ṣe é ní àpẹ̀ẹrẹ rere fún àwọn ọmọ ’Isrọ̄’īl.<sup>1</sup>","[1] Nígbà tí Allāhu - Ọba tó ga jùlọ - fi iná wíwọ̀ rínlẹ̀ fún àwọn òrìṣà àti àwọn abọ̀rìṣà wọn, ìyẹn nínú sūrah al-’Ambiyā’; 21:98-100, àwọn abọ̀rìṣà náà bá mú ọ̀rọ̀ ‘Īsā ọmọ Mọryam - kí ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - wá gẹ́gẹ́ bí àpẹ̀ẹrẹ òrìṣà àkúnlẹ̀bọ tó máa wọná. Allāhu sì ṣàfọ̀mọ́ ‘Īsā ọmọ Mọryam - kí ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - fúnra Rẹ̀ pé kò sọra rẹ̀ d’òòṣà, àmọ́ àwọn tí wọ́n sọ ọ́ d’òòṣà nìkan ló máa wọná."
  43,60,"Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé A bá fẹ́, A ìbá máa fi àwọn mọlāika rọ́pò yín lórí ilẹ̀.",""
